    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚七大集团出资12亿美元收购Boral的完全控制权</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/australias-seven-group-offers-12-bln-full-control-boral-2024-02-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚多元化投资者七集团控股公司（Seven Group Holdings）已出价 19 亿澳元（12.4 亿美元），以完全控制建筑产品集团制造商 Boral，押注澳大利亚基础设施支出热潮将在未来几年得以维持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/australias-seven-group-offers-12-bln-full-control-boral-2024-02-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 22:31:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国将放宽尾气排放规定，减缓电动汽车转型至 2030 年</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/biden-administration-relax-ev-rule-tailpipe-emissions-ny-times-2024-02-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名消息人士周日告诉路透社，美国总统乔·拜登政府将放宽其全面计划中提出的到 2030 年的年度要求，以积极减少尾气排放并提高电动汽车销量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/biden-administration-relax-ev-rule-tailpipe-emissions-ny-times-2024-02-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 15:46:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
